Special Programming
Burris

relative addressing (pg 170)
	int i,
	*ipointer,		// Indirect reference!
	**ippointer;		// Double indirect reference!

	i = 1234;
	ipointer = &i;
	ippointer = &ipointer;

	copy one string to another (pg 179)
		while(*copy++ = *original++);
		goes char by char to copy over